OL,3,CHigh school students learn about death
OL,4,Cand grieving as part of special course
OL,6,FKirstie said: "It's hard to lose
OL,7,Fanyone in your life, no matter what
OL,8,Fage you are. You grow with your grief,
OL,9,Fyou don't get used to it.
OL,11,F"You get on with it, basically - it's
OL,12,Fall you really can do."
OL,14,FThe English curriculum is set to
OL,15,Finclude bereavement training, but no
OL,16,Fequivalent is planned in Scotland.
OL,17,FThis course has so far been given in
OL,18,Ffour Scottish schools.
