OL,6,FAlister Cathro, a teacher at Castle
OL,7,FDouglas High School, told ITV Border:
OL,8,F"I would encourage all schools to try
OL,9,Fand involve themselves in the
OL,10,Fprogramme.
OL,12,F"I think we'll look at it as an
OL,13,Finduction activity, for all of our S5
OL,14,Fand S6 (pupils) going forward."
